'''''tennoio''''' means "for ever" in [[Quenya]].<ref name=C>{{UT|Cirion}}, Author's Note 43</ref>
==Etymology==
*''[[tenna]]'' + ''[[oio]]''<ref name=C/>
==Examples==
"...''[[i]] [[Ilúvatar|Eru]] i [[or]] [[ilya|ilyë]] [[mahalma]]r [[ea (verb)|eä]] '''tennoio'''''" ("the One who is above all thrones '''for ever'''")<ref name=C/>
